Name: 7.62x51mm M948
Description: Damage: 53    Penetration: 78                                                                                                                The M948 caliber depleted uranium armor-piercing round is used to engage light armored vehicles, aircraft, and other heavily armored targets. The bullet features a polymer ballistic tip covering a smaller diameter depleted uranium penetrator, providing high velocity and considerable penetration due to its lighter weight and smaller diameter.
